ct) are not automatically punished by the state, but can be enforced through civil procedure.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>","longitude":null,"slug":"crime-courts","permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/topic\/crime-courts\/","related_topics_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/?related_to=1","twitter_username":null,"items_resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/?topics=1","image_credit":"Photo: <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Crime\">Wikipedia<\/a>","id":1,"kind":"vertical","placetype":"","links":"","name":"crime & courts","category":"Topic","item_count":43384,"woeid":null,"muted_by_default":false,"image_url":"http:\/\/upload.wikimedia.org\/wikipedia\/commons\/4\/4b\/Pierre-Paul_Prud%27hon_-_Justice_and_Divine_Vengeance_Pursuing_Crime.JPG","created_on":"2012-11-28T17:18:53","recent_count":13,"latitude":null,"daily_count":81,"livevideo":"","facebookchat":""}],"date_ap":"Jun 11, 2014, 07:21 PM GMT","status":"published","resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/396271\/","local_url":"\/item\/2014\/06\/11\/troutdale-ore-police-say-they-are-not-aware-of","permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/item\/2014\/06\/11\/troutdale-ore-police-say-they-are-not-aware-of","media":null,"tweet":null,"updated_date":"2014-06-11T19:21:39.662510","type":"text","pushed":true,"data":null,"submitter":"editor","date":"2014-06-11T19:21:35.376958","content":"Troutdale, Ore., police say they are not aware of any prior problems with gunman Jared Padgett - @maxoregonian","url_domain":null,"author":{"last_name":"Johnson","first_name":"Grace","email":"grace.johnson@breakingnews.com","is_staff":true,"username":"grace.johnson","resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/user\/11\/","id":11},"whoas":12,"note":null,"source":null,"id":396271,"slug":"troutdale-ore-police-say-they-are-not-aware-of","url":"","shortened_url":null,"push_content":"Troutdale, Ore., police say they are not aware of any prior problems with gunman Jared Padgett - @maxoregonian"},{"data_type":null,"importance":2,"short_permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/i\/BpEw","