guilty, the offender may be sentenced to punishment such as community sentence, imprisonment, life imprisonment or, in some jurisdictions, even death.<\/p>\n<p>To be classified as a crime, the act of doing something bad (actus reus) must be usually accompanied by the intention to do something bad (mens rea), with certain exceptions (strict liability).<\/p>\n<p>While every crime violates the law, not every violation of the law counts as a crime. Breaches of private law (torts and breaches of contract) are not automatically punished by the state, but can be enforced through civil procedure.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>","longitude":null,"slug":"crime-courts","permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/topic\/crime-courts\/","related_topics_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/?related_to=1","twitter_username":null,"items_resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/?topics=1","image_credit":"Photo: <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Crime\">Wikipedia<\/a>","id":1,"kind":"vertical","placetype":"","links":"","name":"crime & courts","category":"Topic","item_count":43384,"woeid":null,"muted_by_default":false,"image_url":"http:\/\/upload.wikimedia.org\/wikipedia\/commons\/4\/4b\/Pierre-Paul_Prud%27hon_-_Justice_and_Divine_Vengeance_Pursuing_Crime.JPG","created_on":"2012-11-28T17:18:53","recent_count":13,"latitude":null,"daily_count":81,"livevideo":"","facebookchat":""}],"date_ap":"Jun 11, 2014, 06:20 PM GMT","status":"published","resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/396225\/","local_url":"\/item\/2014\/06\/11\/reynolds-high-school-gunman-obtained-weapons-from","permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/item\/2014\/06\/11\/reynolds-high-school-gunman-obtained-weapons-from","media":null,"tweet":null,"updated_date":"2014-06-11T18:20:42.366856","type":"text","pushed":true,"data":null,"submitter":"editor","date":"2014-06-11T18:20:38.180050","content":"Reynolds High School gunman obtained weapons from his family home - @NBCNews live video","url_domain":null,"author":{"last_name":"Johnson","first_name":"Grace","ema