fender may be sentenced to punishment such as community sentence, imprisonment, life imprisonment or, in some jurisdictions, even death.<\/p>\n<p>To be classified as a crime, the act of doing something bad (actus reus) must be usually accompanied by the intention to do something bad (mens rea), with certain exceptions (strict liability).<\/p>\n<p>While every crime violates the law, not every violation of the law counts as a crime. Breaches of private law (torts and breaches of contract) are not automatically punished by the state, but can be enforced through civil procedure.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>","longitude":null,"slug":"crime-courts","permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/topic\/crime-courts\/","related_topics_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/?related_to=1","twitter_username":null,"items_resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/?topics=1","image_credit":"Photo: <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Crime\">Wikipedia<\/a>","id":1,"kind":"vertical","placetype":"","links":"","name":"crime & courts","category":"Topic","item_count":43384,"woeid":null,"muted_by_default":false,"image_url":"http:\/\/upload.wikimedia.org\/wikipedia\/commons\/4\/4b\/Pierre-Paul_Prud%27hon_-_Justice_and_Divine_Vengeance_Pursuing_Crime.JPG","created_on":"2012-11-28T17:18:53","recent_count":13,"latitude":null,"daily_count":81,"livevideo":"","facebookchat":""}],"date_ap":"Jun 11, 2014, 12:13 AM GMT","status":"published","resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/395914\/","local_url":"\/item\/2014\/06\/11\/police-reynolds-high-school-in-troutdale-ore-s","permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/item\/2014\/06\/11\/police-reynolds-high-school-in-troutdale-ore-s","media":null,"tweet":null,"updated_date":"2014-06-11T00:13:26.208864","type":"text","pushed":true,"data":null,"submitter":"editor","date":"2014-06-11T00:13:21.205950","content":"Police: Reynolds High School in Troutdale, Ore., shut down until further notice after school shooting - @Oregonian live video","url_domain":null,"author":{"last_name":"Stampher","first