thods are employed in politics, which include promoting one's own political views among people, negotiation with other political subjects, making laws, and exercising force, including warfare against adversaries. Politics is exercised on a wide range of social levels, from clans and tribes of traditional societies, through modern local governments, companies and institutions up to sovereign states, to the international level.<\/p>\n<p>A political system is a framework which defines acceptable political methods within a given society. History of political thought can be traced back to early antiquity, with seminal works such as Plato's <i>Republic<\/i>, Aristotle's <i>Politics<\/i> and the works of Confucius.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>","longitude":null,"slug":"politics","permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/topic\/politics\/","related_topics_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/?related_to=2","twitter_username":"breakingpol","items_resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/?topics=2","image_credit":"<a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Politics\">Wikipedia<\/a>","id":2,"kind":"vertical","placetype":"","links":"","name":"politics","category":"Topic","item_count":45446,"woeid":null,"muted_by_default":false,"image_url":"http:\/\/upload.wikimedia.org\/wikipedia\/commons\/6\/6a\/Inglehart_Values_Map.svg","created_on":"2012-10-23T22:09:19","recent_count":11,"latitude":null,"daily_count":41,"livevideo":"","facebookchat":""}],"date_ap":"Jun 10, 2014, 10:58 PM GMT","status":"published","resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/395869\/","local_url":"\/item\/2014\/06\/10\/rep-earl-blumenauer-d-ore-leads-us-house-in-mo","permalink":"http:\/\/www.breakingnews.com\/item\/2014\/06\/10\/rep-earl-blumenauer-d-ore-leads-us-house-in-mo","media":null,"tweet":null,"updated_date":"2014-06-10T22:58:51.729290","type":"text","pushed":false,"data":null,"submitter":"editor","date":"2014-06-10T22:58:44.188486","content":"Rep. Earl Blumenauer, D-Ore., leads US House in moment of silence for victims of school shooting in Oreg